description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for an enthusiastic and motivated Band 5 Staff Nurse position on Gowers Ward. Gowers Ward is a 30 bed ward specialising in both acute Neurology- providing a Regional service from south west to mid Wales and Respiratory medicine. Neurology is a fascinating speciality, where patients are admitted for diagnostics as either elective for ongoing investigations or emergency transfers into the hospital and from acute areas such as ITU. The ward has very close working relationships with both medical and multi disciplinary team members throughout the patients journey. The ward offers a challenging environment with various learning opportunities and additional training/ support for both registered and newly registered nurses to develop and progress in their career.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; English and/or Welsh speakers are equally welcome to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
